ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of RITA TSANG of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Montie Brewer.
